text.__SUMMARY__: Eulimastoma eutropia is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Pyramidellidae, the pyrams and their allies.
text.Description: The length of the shell varies between 2.5 mm and 4.3 mm.
text.Distribution: This marine species occurs of Southeast Asia and the Philippines.
